  DisplayText: "Loftj\xE1rn is an ancient rock that landed at our village during
    the Great War. Bjorn the Unbroken harvested some to craft his legendy blade during
    those times. Since then our people have preserved it. It is an important landmark
    in the village, no weapons have been crafted from it since."
